data.description: This Is The One! Great home for your growing family!  Schools and parks in walking distance!  Grocery shopping, restaurants, eateries, boutiques, and spas within a few miles is just a small perk of what the City of Florissant has to offer!  Theatre events, festivals, parades, and community are treasured in the lovely neighborhood!  Once you get into the house notice the beautiful ceramic tile and hardwood flooring!  Living room dining room combination! Eat-in kitchen and a finished basement containing motion-censored lighting and two bonus rooms!  Spacious yard for entertainment, stainless steel appliances, primary bedroom with bathroom, and plenty of storage space!  The seller is offering a one-year free American Home Shield home warranty and a $2500 credit at closing for paint! Schedule your showing today!
